</sup>
<ul>
<li>The meter is the basic unit of length measurement in the metric system.=
 Written as a base 10 exponent, <span class=3D"mwe-math-element"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;" =
