</sup>
<ul><li>Write 2,600 nm as =E2=80=9C2,600. nm=E2=80=9D with a decimal point.=
 Then move the decimal as follows:
<ul>
<li>260.0=E2=80=A6=E2=80=A6=E2=80=A6. (one space left)</li>
